  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/README
  /usr/share/doc/glitz-0.4.4/TODO

Files included in the libglitz1 package:

  /usr/bin/cygglitz-1.dll

Files included in the libglitz-glx1 package:

  /usr/bin/cygglitz-glx-1.dll

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 0.4.4-3 -----
Reverting because cairo-1.0.4 will not compile against 0.5.3.
Built against modular X11.

----- version 0.5.3-1 -----
Version bump.
Includes the new Win32 OpenGL backend in the libglitz1 package, 
as it has no extra cygwin dependencies.

----- version 0.4.4-2 -----
Libraries repackaged in separate libglitz1 and libglitz-glx1 packages.

----- version 0.4.4-1 -----
Upstream version bump.
Shared libraries are now available in a separate libglitz1 package.

----- version 0.3.0-1 -----
CVS snapshot from 20050115, based on the Gentoo Linux ebuild.

----- version 0.2.3-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://cygwinports.dotsrc.net/
